description = "A haggard man in his forties who has aged twenty years in the past six months. His once-fine clothes are stained and torn, his eyes hollow from sleepless nights. When the ghost pirates came, he refused to flee like the other nobles, choosing to stay with his people. Now he commands what remains of Larton's defenses from a fortified hideout, desperately hoping someone will answer his call for help. His hands shake when he speaks of the horrors he has witnessed."
